Click on the  red button above to download  the Zip file That contain all the logos needed for the the dashboard


STEP 1: Create The Title
      1) Click on the "Text Box" Button on the ribbon to add a text box to the report .  
  • Apply those changes:   


     2)Type in the box "TSA Claims - Cost Per Claim Analysis"

     3)  Font: Arial Black     ,      4)  Size:  28     ,      5)   Bold          ,   6)   Center             , 7)  Color # 12239E

                                                                                          

  • Fix the  box Size:  
                7)   Weight :   1047                                                     8)    Height :    72



  • Make a Border with light gray  color and  radius = 10 



STEP 2:  Load The Logos 

  1. Click Insert from the panel.
  2.  Select Image Option.
  3. Look for your file.
  4. Select TSA Logo.


           5. Repeat the same process to get colaberry Logo.
           6. Display both logos on the side of the title like it shown bellow.
           7. Select Both logo and click bring forward.
